head_commit.message:
Fix: refresh-stocks-portfolio curl timeouts (exit 28) abort job

All curl calls in command substitutions now use '|| true' to prevent set -e from aborting the script on timeout. Added continue-on-error: true to Seed, Stats, Verify dashboard, and Verify dividend steps so a single timeout cannot skip all subsequent steps.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>

head_commit.message:
Fix: daily_refresh timeout (exit 28) - retry loop broken by set -e

The retry loop never reached attempt 2+ because curl exit code 28 (timeout) aborted the script under set -e. Added || true to curl, empty response handling, increased timeouts (120s->180s, job 10->20min), and added set_time_limit(300) + per-call stream timeouts in the PHP endpoint.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
